<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1395] InfoServers no longer put up a UI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1395</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;InfoServers do not work in an vanilla Hadoop 0.20 and HBase 0.20-dev installation. Directory listings instead of UI.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;CentOS 5.3 x86_64, JDK 1.6.0_13-b03&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12424971">HBASE-1395</key>
            <summary>InfoServers no longer put up a UI</summary>
